 
<p>
Complaints from black immigrants in US deportation prison *reveal a
disturbing pattern of <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2022/jul/22/ice-black-immigrants-abuse-medical-neglect">physical abuse and ignoring medical needs</a>.*
<p>
An indigenous prisoner in Australian jail died of a disease that
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2022/jul/22/indigenous-death-in-nsw-jail-from-ear-infection-the-result-of-systemic-failures-coroner">proper medical procedures would have identified</a>.
But they don't follow proper medical procedures with indigenous
prisoners.

 